focus the Tamer chip fall down to the earth and turns to dust.

::Inu-Yasha::

he did it He is True Silver Dragon Master." Inu scans his power as he see 
Koj's running off of pure emotion that is power starts to equal Inu and 
continue to grow as it doubles. "This should be a good match."

::Koj::

Koj looks at Prebon as a calm blue Ki seems to whril around him as his 
should plates gain the Seal of the Silver Dragon. "Prebon are you ready for 
your final journey." Koj Fires of his jets streams toward the earth looking 
like a blue shooting star as increase speed to a extreme level as swings the 
Fang with all his might trying slice Prebon chest open. "Only I control my 
destiny and this is the end of yours."
